data.title: Texas Counties: Land Area
data.meta_description: Texas counties listed in order of land area as of the 2010 U.S. Census.
data.text:
Land area does not include bodies of water. Some counties may appear larger on the map than their ranking would suggest due to the presence of lakes and rivers.
